reviewText: loves my mama Patti! i've cooked some recipes outta this cookbook. thank you Mama Patti!

I love this dvd. Patti is a true gem. Her cooking tips are amazing and her personality makes the video more engaging. Ms. Patti is a real woman and I love it. Please make more dvds for us, Ms. Patti :-)

Patti La Belle,
Is known for her soul full  cooking skills ! For the price of the DVD & dated , I was not expecting all of her trade  secrets  , but this DVD was really an info- commercial for her line of hot sauces & spices !

I am a big fan of Miss Patti LaBelle and have her previous cookbooks.  So when I saw that she had a DVD out I had to purchase it.  The DVD is just like a Food Network cook show, plus she shows you how she decorates for her dinner guests.  Cudos to Miss LaBelle....
THis was a great DVD. Love Ms Patti and how she carefully explained the cooking directions and most of all how it can be altered for people with Diabetes and HBP.
